&lt;p&gt;The&lt;strong&gt; Installation Technician&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;will plan and perform security system installations, corrective maintenance, troubleshooting and demolition tasks. Security systems include access control systems, burglar alarm systems, IP Cameras and other electronic and physical security systems.&lt;/p&gt;
