&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High school diploma or state-recognized equivalent.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 3 years of security installation experience and network ability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledgeable of security equipment systems (i.e., intrusion detection, assessment, and access control).&lt;/li&gt;
