&lt;li&gt;&amp;nbsp;Works directly with staff to ensure the PACS server has the latest server patches and ensures that planned system maintenance is completed during acceptable time periods to prevent interruptions to government operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
